Ubuntu 14.04 Pentaho Report Desginer 使用
运行报表设计工具
cd /usr/report-designer
./report-designer.sh

报错:
Error connecting to database [report] : org.pentaho.di.core.exception.KettleDatabaseException: 
Error occurred while trying to connect to the database

Driver class 'org.gjt.mm.mysql.Driver' could not be found, make sure the 'MySQL' driver (jar file) is installed.
org.gjt.mm.mysql.Driver


org.pentaho.di.core.exception.KettleDatabaseException: 
Error occurred while trying to connect to the database

Driver class 'org.gjt.mm.mysql.Driver' could not be found, make sure the 'MySQL' driver (jar file) is installed.
org.gjt.mm.mysql.Driver
	...................
	at org.pentaho.di.core.database.Database.connectUsingClass(Database.java:466)
	... 124 more

Hostname       : localhost
Port           : 3306
Database name  : report

网上查了解决方案,都是在Windows系统下,有的说把数据库驱动放到lib文件夹的ext文件夹目录下
➜  report-designer  tree -L 1
.
├── ChangeLog.txt
├── configuration-template
├── docs
├── launcher.jar
├── launcher.properties
├── lib
├── PentahoReporting_OSS_Licenses.html
├── plugins
├── README.txt
├── report-designer.bat
├── report-designer.sh
├── resources
├── samples
├── set-pentaho-env.bat
├── set-pentaho-env.sh
└── templates
因为之前装过idea,所以直接到idea的目录下拷贝了驱动
➜  ~  cd ~/.IntelliJIdea14/config/jdbc-drivers 
➜  jdbc-drivers  ls
mysql-connector-java-5.1.35-bin.jar  postgresql-9.4-1201.jdbc4.jar
mysql-connector-license.txt          postgresql-driver-license.txt
➜  jdbc-drivers  sudo cp mysql-connector-java-5.1.35-bin.jar /usr/qunar/report-designer/lib/ext/

重启发现还是报错,最后去看了一下这个目录结构,发现lib下有个jdbc的目录,进去一看,发现啥数据库的驱动都有,就是没有mysql的,fuck!!!!!
拷进去,重启,然后Test,搞定
![]()

新建一条查询语句,现在report库里止呕一个数据表syscode_business_type
点击右上角的Add Query新建一条查询语句
![]()
第一次无法预览,需要先编辑,然后直接点OK就可以了,回到原来的界面就可以预览了


